9 An Act relating to the State Treasurer; authorizing
the Treasurer to create, operate, or contract for the
10 operation of a depository and issue certain
transaction cards; requiring the Treasurer to provide
11 certain procedures and develop fee structure upon
certain circumstance; stipulating certain deposits
12 and transactions be considered the exchange of legal
